summary: This is a court subpoena issued by the U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York to the Massachusetts Registry of Vital Records, commanding them to appear and produce a birth certificate for an individual (name redacted) in the case United States v. Ghislaine Maxwell. The subpoena is signed by U.S. Attorney Audrey Strauss.

keyFacts: The U.S. Attorney's Office subpoenaed the Massachusetts Registry of Vital Records for a birth certificate related to the Ghislaine Maxwell criminal case.
The subpoena was issued by U.S. Attorney Audrey Strauss on July 19, 2021, with a court appearance scheduled for November 29, 2021.
The birth certificate is for an individual whose name is redacted in the document, indicated as 'N.' • • -(DOR 1'.
